folder: Ashford Street & Linden Boulevard, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Ashford Street, (foreground not shown), between Linden Boulevard and Stanley Avenue (right). In the background on the east side of Elton Street is seen the I. R. T. yards. Cleveland Street extends north and south in the center of the view.
July 5, 1934
P. L. Sperr

folder: Ashford Street & Linden Boulevard, Brooklyn, NY
text:
Ashford Street, west side, north from Linden Blvd., showing gardens in the foreground, and the farm house at 816 Hegeman Ave., in the rear backgrouud In the extreme background, way be seen the I.R.T. New Lots Ave., Lines.
July 5, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
